thread.title: Princes Harry and William go on Windsor walkabout to greet fans before wedding

title: Princes Harry and William go on Windsor walkabout to greet fans before wedding
text:
May 18, 2018 / 5:02 PM / Updated 35 minutes ago Princes Harry and William go on Windsor walkabout to greet fans before wedding Reuters Staff 1 Britain’s Prince Harry and elder brother, Prince William, left to greet royal fans ahead of Harry’s wedding on Saturday to U.S. actress Meghan Markle. Britain's Princes Harry and William greet Harry's REUTERS/Dylan Martinez
To loud cheers from the crowd, Harry emerged from the castle wearing a grey jacket, white shirt and slacks. He was given a teddy bear by one fan.
Outside the Horse and Groom pub, Harry shook hands with fans and spoke to children in the crowd while well-wishers filmed his every move on their telephones. Reporting by Guy Faulconbridge; editing by Michael Holden
